==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# [[vegetarian|Vegetarian]] and / or [[vegan]]; a person who may either eat no animal flesh or eat no animal products at all.

===Usage===
''Veg*n'' does not distinguish between vegetarian or vegan. It is likely to be used when the person being described is of [[indeterminate]] status, or when refering to a group of people that includes both vegetarians and vegans.

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

#Relating to vegetarians and / or vegans.
#Relating to vegetarianism and / or veganism.

===Etymology===
Derived from ''[[vegan]]'' and ''[[vegetarian]]'' and the use in [[computer language]]s of [[*]] as a [[wildcard]]

===Derived terms===
*[[veg*nism]]

